projects.title: FILTER COFFEE BEANS
projects.subtitle: COLOMBIA Finca La Esperanza
projects.description: In the diverse department of Nariño, in the south west of Colombia, bordering Ecuador and the Pacific Ocean, there is a municipality named Consacá. In the vereda (or township) of La Aguada, Jesús Ignacio Paredes cultivates approximately one hectare made up of three separate plots named La Esperanza.
